# Deployment Details

## Frontend (Web Project)

Codebase / Upload Directory:
/home/root1/

Live Website Path:
/var/www/aivlm.org/

Frontend Deployment Steps:
scp -P 22 browser.zip root1@103.117.51.74:/home/root1/
sudo rm -rf /var/www/aivlm.org/*
sudo cp ~/browser.zip /var/www/aivlm.org/
cd /var/www/aivlm.org
sudo unzip browser.zip
sudo systemctl reload nginx

--------------------------------------------------

## Backend Project

Codebase / Upload Directory:
/home/root1/

Live Backend Code Path:
/var/opt/mahasabha-backend/

Check Backend Files:
ls -l /var/opt/mahasabha-backend/

Backend Deployment Steps:
cd /var/opt/mahasabha-backend/
git pull origin main
pm2 restart mahasabha-backend

Backend Process Manager:
Using PM2 tool we are running this project.

--------------------------------------------------

## Database & File Storage

Database Used:
MongoDB(No passoword for DB)

Image / Photo Storage Path:
/var/opt/mahasabha-backend/uploads/

All uploaded images and photos are stored inside the backend project uploads folder.

